Port from [Steps/5.md](Steps/5.md) and [Steps/6.md](Steps/6.md):

- Cylindrical stock when turning is active, block stock otherwise
- Material density lookup → weight in kg
- Engineer override support (accept `override_kg` parameter)

**Functions:** `estimate_stock(geometry, routing, material) → StockEstimate`

