## Verification Plan

### Automated
- Start server: `cd backend && python main.py`
- Test each API endpoint with `curl` or browser devtools
- Verify JSON responses match Pydantic schemas

### Manual
- Click through all 3 sample parts end-to-end
- Verify all dashboard numbers update dynamically
- Verify DFM simulation produces different values
- Verify routing toggles affect downstream calculations
